reviewText: I am surprised that I should be asked to review this, er, product. I had to change my user name to one which affords some degree of anonymity to do so. Having done so let me say that it is a heartbreaking work of staggering genius. Or something. Actually it is just fine except that the men are, shall we say, over-endowed. Who ordered that? But the important thing is that everybody has fun and no one gets hurt. So there you are.
